{{short description|Paleochristian sarcophagus}}
[[File:Sarcófago paleocristiano de Layos, Toledo.jpg|thumb|Layos Sarcophagus in Toledo]]

'''Layos Sarcophagus''' is a [[paleochristian]] [[sarcophagus]] found in [[Layos, Toledo]] in 1627.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rah.es/sarcofago-paleocristiano/ |title=Sarcófago paleocristiano de Layos |date=29 January 2015 |access-date=29 September 2018 |work=[[Real Academia de la Historia]] |language=es}}</ref> It is kept at the [[Museu Frederic Marès]].<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.europapress.es/castilla-lamancha/noticia-cultura-encarga-dos-reproducciones-sarcofago-layos-toledo-disfrute-region-20070819190139.html |title=Cultura encarga dos reproducciones del sarcófago de Layos (Toledo) para su disfrute en la región |location=Toledo |date=19 August 2007 |access-date=29 September 2018 |newspaper=[[Europa Press (news agency)|Europa Press]]}}</ref> It is focused on the [[dogma]] of the [[Incarnation (Christianity)|Incarnation]], and it is opposed of the [[docetism]] and [[monophysitism]].<ref>{{cite book |last=Núñez Rodríguez |first=Manuel |chapter=El arte paleocristiano y bizantino |title=Historia del Arte: La Edad Media |volume=2 |editor-first=Isidro |editor-last=Bango Torviso |editor2-first=Gonzalo M. |editor2-last=Borrás Gualis |editor3-first=Isabel |editor3-last=Cervera Fernández |editor4-first=Clara |editor4-last=Delgado Valero |editor5-first=Sue-Hee |editor5-last=Kim |editor6-first=Joaquín |editor6-last=Yarza Luaces |url=https://books.google.es/books?id=pdiabtSJ_tEC |publisher=[[Alianza Editorial]] |page=8 |year=1996 |isbn=978-84-206-9482-5}}</ref>

In October 2007 a replica was shown at the Museo de los Concilios y de la Cultura Visigoda in [[Castilla La Mancha]].<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.abc.es/hemeroteca/historico-05-10-2007/abc/Toledo/la-replica-del-sarcofago-de-layos-en-el-museo-de-los-concilios_1641062745165.html |title=La réplica del sarcófago de Layos, en el Museo de los Concilios |date=5 October 2007 |access-date=29 September 2018 |newspaper=[[ABC (Spain)|ABC]] |language=es}}</ref>

